pure_test.bas - demonstrate irrlicht_c functional, not require any "bi" includes

const.bi - include with some constants from Irrlicht Engine SDK for FreeBASIC

irrlicht_c.bi - automatic generated include with all irrlicht_c imported functions

irrlicht.bi - include with object oriented implementation Irrlicht Engine SDK for FreeBASIC

HelloWorld.bas - one-to-one demo from Irrlicht Engine SDK, require "irrlicht.bi" include

test.bas - demonstrate IEventReceiver, require "irrlicht.bi" include

class_templates - directory with automatic generated template include files for object oriented programming, not include to SVN, can be found on download page with irrlicht_c_fb archive

h2bi.py - Python script for automatic generation, in future must be replaced with FreeBasic
